{
  "dashboard": {
    "title": "Unraid Monitoring - Home",
    "tags": ["home", "overview"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "30s",
    "time": {
      "from": "now-1h",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "üè† Welcome to Unraid Monitoring",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "## Quick Navigation\n\nüëâ **[System Overview](#)** | **[Docker Containers](#)** | **[GPU Monitoring](#)** | **[Array Health](#)** | **[Hardware Sensors](#)**\n\n---\n\nThis dashboard provides a quick overview of your Unraid server. Click the links above or use the dashboard selector (top-left) to view detailed metrics."
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Array Status",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 4},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "unraid_array_state{array=\"md\"}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {
                "type": "value",
                "options": {
                  "0": {"text": "STOPPED", "color": "red"},
                  "1": {"text": "STARTED", "color": "green"}
                }
              }
            ],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "red"},
                {"value": 1, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "textMode": "value_and_name",
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "none"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "CPU Usage",
        "type": "gauge",
        "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 4, "y": 4},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "100 - (avg by (instance) (irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[5m])) * 100)",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Memory Usage",
        "type": "gauge",
        "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 9, "y": 4},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "(1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes)) * 100",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 90, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "GPU Temperature",
        "type": "gauge",
        "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 14, "y": 4},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "nvidia_gpu_temperature_celsius",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "celsius",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 85, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Running Containers",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 5, "x": 19, "y": 4},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "count(container_last_seen{name!=\"\"})",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "textMode": "value_and_name",
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "area"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "üñ•Ô∏è System Overview",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### System Resources\n\nView detailed CPU, memory, disk I/O, and network statistics.\n\n**[‚û°Ô∏è Open System Overview Dashboard](#)**"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "title": "üê≥ Docker Containers",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### Container Monitoring\n\nTrack CPU, memory, network, and disk usage for all containers.\n\n**[‚û°Ô∏è Open Docker Dashboard](#)**"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "title": "üíæ Array Health",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### Unraid Array Status\n\nMonitor disk health, SMART data, parity checks, and array status.\n\n**[‚û°Ô∏è Open Array Health Dashboard](#)**"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "title": "üéÆ GPU Monitoring",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### NVIDIA GPU Stats\n\nView GPU temperature, utilization, memory, and power consumption.\n\n**[‚û°Ô∏è Open GPU Dashboard](#)**"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "CPU & Memory Trends",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "100 - (avg by (instance) (irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[5m])) * 100)",
            "legendFormat": "CPU Usage %",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "(1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes)) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Memory Usage %",
            "refId": "B"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
            "custom": {
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 12,
        "title": "Network Traffic",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(irate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{device!~\"lo|veth.*|br.*|docker.*\"}[5m])) * 8",
            "legendFormat": "Receive",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(irate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{device!~\"lo|veth.*|br.*|docker.*\"}[5m])) * 8 * -1",
            "legendFormat": "Transmit",
            "refId": "B"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "bps",
            "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"},
            "custom": {
              "fillOpacity": 10,
              "showPoints": "never"
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 13,
        "title": "Disk Temperatures",
        "type": "bargauge",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "unraid_disk_smart_temperature_celsius",
            "legendFormat": "{{disk}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "celsius",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 70,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 40, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 50, "color": "orange"},
                {"value": 60, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "orientation": "horizontal",
          "displayMode": "gradient",
          "showUnfilled": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 14,
        "title": "Disk Space Usage",
        "type": "bargauge",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "(unraid_disk_used_bytes / unraid_disk_size_bytes) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "{{disk}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "green"},
                {"value": 70, "color": "yellow"},
                {"value": 85, "color": "orange"},
                {"value": 95, "color": "red"}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "orientation": "horizontal",
          "displayMode": "gradient",
          "showUnfilled": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 15,
        "title": "üìä Quick Stats",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 30},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "node_time_seconds - node_boot_time_seconds",
            "legendFormat": "Uptime",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "count(count(node_cpu_seconds_total) by (cpu))",
            "legendFormat": "CPU Cores",
            "refId": "B"
          },
          {
            "expr": "node_memory_MemTotal_bytes",
            "legendFormat": "Total RAM",
            "refId": "C"
          },
          {
            "expr": "unraid_array_disks_total",
            "legendFormat": "Array Disks",
            "refId": "D"
          },
          {
            "expr": "nvidia_gpu_duty_cycle",
            "legendFormat": "GPU Usage",
            "refId": "E"
          },
          {
            "expr": "count(container_last_seen{name!=\"\"})",
            "legendFormat": "Containers",
            "refId": "F"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {"value": 0, "color": "blue"}
              ]
            }
          },
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Uptime"},
              "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "s"}]
            },
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Total RAM"},
              "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "bytes"}]
            },
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "GPU Usage"},
              "properties": [{"id": "unit", "value": "percent"}]
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "textMode": "value_and_name",
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "orientation": "horizontal"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 16,
        "title": "‚ÑπÔ∏è Help & Information",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 36},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "### Getting Started\n\n**Dashboards:**\n- Use the dashboard selector (üìä icon, top-left) to switch between dashboards\n- All dashboards auto-refresh every 30 seconds\n- Click on any panel to see more details\n\n**Alerts:**\n- Email alerts are configured for critical issues\n- View active alerts: **Alerting** ‚Üí **Alert rules** (left sidebar)\n- Check alert history: **Alerting** ‚Üí **Alert rules** ‚Üí Click on any rule\n\n**Time Range:**\n- Use the time picker (top-right) to change the time range\n- Zoom in on graphs by clicking and dragging\n\n**Useful Links:**\n- üìö [README Documentation](about:blank)\n- ‚öôÔ∏è [Email Alerts Setup](about:blank)\n- üîç [Alert Rules Reference](about:blank)"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "overwrite": true,
  "folderId": null,
  "folderUid": null
}
